        Creates a new LogEntry representing a log with the given time, tag, message, and throwable that was logged at the given level.
        Parameters:
        dateTime - the date and time of the log.
        namespace - the namespace of the logger that emitted the log.
        message - the message for the log.
        throwable - the Throwable associated with the log.
        logLevel - the level the log was logged at.
